# aura-pos-bff

Backend For Frontend — GraphQL layer between `aura-pos-fe` and `pos-service`.

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Environment variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `PORT` | `4000` | BFF server port |
| `POS_SERVICE_URL` | `http://localhost:8080` | Go BE URL |
| `JWT_SECRET` | `secret` | Must match pos-service JWT secret |
| `CORS_ORIGIN` | `http://localhost:5173` | FE dev server URL |

## Endpoints

- `GET  /health` — health check
- `POST /graphql` — GraphQL endpoint

## GraphQL Queries

```graphql
# Login
mutation {
  login(email: "admin@aura-bkk.com", password: "password", tenantId: "aura-bkk") {
    token
    user { id email role tenantId }
  }
}

# Get current user (requires Authorization header)
query {
  me { id email role tenantId }
}

# Get products
query {
  products(tenantId: "aura-bkk") {
    id name price category stock imageUrl
  }
}

# Get branches (admin/manager only)
query {
  branches(tenantId: "aura-bkk") {
    id name address
  }
}
```

## How it connects

```
aura-pos-fe (React)
    ↓  GraphQL  :4000
aura-pos-bff (Node.js)
    ↓  REST     :8080
pos-service (Go + Gin)
    ↓
PostgreSQL
```
